341
00:23:27,530 --> 00:23:31,560
<i>Perhaps our Goryeo is the same.</i>

342
00:23:32,560 --> 00:23:35,480
<i>I will take time to think about this.</i>

343
00:23:46,960 --> 00:23:51,240
I will not have you stand alone in the wilderness.

344
00:23:52,520 --> 00:23:54,910
I will stand together with you.

345
00:23:54,910 --> 00:23:57,730
Then, the engagement must be broken first.

346
00:23:57,730 --> 00:24:00,160
Your marriage with the royal family of Goryeo.

347
00:24:00,160 --> 00:24:02,140
Are you sure you can do it?

348
00:24:02,140 --> 00:24:06,450
- But, that-
- If you wish to stand together in the wilderness as "us,"

349
00:24:06,450 --> 00:24:09,210
