350
00:24:30,170 --> 00:24:34,680
I will not marry Yeongyeongun.

351
00:24:35,640 --> 00:24:37,500
- Pardon?
- What do you mean by this?

352
00:24:37,500 --> 00:24:40,580
I am sorry for not telling you sooner.

353
00:24:40,580 --> 00:24:42,580
But I cannot do this.

354
00:24:43,580 --> 00:24:47,040
Child, why are you acting like this?

355
00:24:47,040 --> 00:24:48,720
Is this because your friend is leaving as a tribute bride?

356
00:24:48,720 --> 00:24:50,560
If so, I will switch her out.

357
00:24:50,560 --> 00:24:53,440
What will you do after you switch her with someone else?

358
00:24:58,810 --> 00:25:01,720
How could you humiliate me like this?

359
00:25:01,720 --> 00:25:03,460
I am sorry.

360
00:25:04,440 --> 00:25:07,320
If you will unilaterally break this marriage,

361
00:25:07,320 --> 00:25:10,220
I will not just sit idly by, either.

362
00:25:10,220 --> 00:25:12,050
What do you want me to do?

363
00:25:12,050 --> 00:25:13,620
How shall I take responsibility for this?

364
00:25:13,620 --> 00:25:16,890
I will make sure your father and your younger brothers

365
00:25:16,890 --> 00:25:19,890
