366
00:25:21,590 --> 00:25:23,580
If so, Father,

367
00:25:23,580 --> 00:25:25,900
cast me out.

368
00:25:25,900 --> 00:25:30,320
Cast me out of the Min family.

369
00:25:37,900 --> 00:25:39,540
Noonim!

