<i>By the time you read this letter, I will break off the engagement with Yeongyeongun.</i>

372
00:26:16,920 --> 00:26:19,200
<i>Since this is breaking an engagement with the royal family,</i>

373
00:26:19,200 --> 00:26:22,650
<i>I will definitely face negative consequences for it.</i>

374
00:26:22,650 --> 00:26:26,630
<i>However, I will not run from it.</i>

375
00:26:26,630 --> 00:26:29,250
<i>I want to meet with you, Young Master.</i>

